        "Header": "From Pitch to Script",
        "Text": "The premise for Charlie X originated in Gene Roddenberry’s early series pitch under the working title The Day Charlie Became God. The idea was later developed into a teleplay by D. C. Fontana, marking one of her key early contributions to Star Trek."
